---
title: Savoury Pork Steak & Herby Mayo with Potato Mash & Sautéed Bacon Greens
description: Treat yourself to the ultimate comfort meal with a gourmet twist! Juicy pork steak takes the stage, with our savoury seasoning mix adding tons of flavour. On the side, we’ve got buttery potato mash for that perfect, cosy base and sautéed greens to keep things fresh and vibrant.
